/* Legal */
"legal.section" = "Legal";
"legal.privacy.title" = "Privacy Policy";
"legal.terms.title" = "Terms of Service";
"legal.privacy.content" = "AiQo Privacy Policy\n\nLast updated: March 2026\n\n1. Data We Collect\nWe collect health data (steps, calories, sleep, heart rate) from Apple HealthKit with your permission. We also collect profile information you provide (name, age, height, weight).\n\n2. How We Use Your Data\nHealth data is used solely to provide personalized insights and coaching within the app. We never sell your data to third parties.\n\n3. Data Storage\nHealth data is stored locally on your device. Data sent to AI services is processed without permanent storage.\n\n4. Third-Party Sharing\nWe do not share your personal data with any third party without your explicit consent.\n\n5. Your Rights\nYou can delete your data at any time from the app settings. You can revoke HealthKit permissions from device settings.\n\n6. Contact Us\nFor privacy inquiries, reach out through the app.";
"legal.terms.content" = "AiQo Terms of Service\n\nLast updated: March 2026\n\n1. Acceptance\nBy using AiQo, you agree to these terms.\n\n2. Service\nAiQo provides health tracking and AI-powered coaching. Content is not a substitute for professional medical advice.\n\n3. Subscriptions\n- Free trial: 7 days\n- Individual plan: $5.99/month\n- Family plan: $10.00/month (up to 5 people)\nSubscriptions do not auto-renew. Each cycle is 30 days.\n\n4. User Conduct\nYou are responsible for your use of the app and any content you post in the Tribe feature.\n\n5. Disclaimer\nAiQo does not provide medical advice. Consult your doctor before making health decisions based on app data.\n\n6. Changes\nWe reserve the right to modify these terms at any time.";

